  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1890",
  "title": "How CurrentRefinements works",
  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\nFeature || Bug\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the current behavior?**\r\nAssume that we have 2 refinements. Then current refinements can be:\r\nA: A1, A2, A3\r\nB: B1, B2\r\n\r\nIf I remove B1 (by clicking on CurrentRefinements component), then all A refinements (A1, A2, A3) will be removed automatically too.\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the expected behavior?**\r\nIt should only remove B1, right?\r\n\r\n**What project are you opening an issue for?**\r\n- react-instantsearch\r\n\r\n**What is the version you are using? Always use the latest one before opening a bug issue.**\r\n2.1.0\r\n",
